Package org.jetel.lookup

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DBLookup
    DBLookup that performs data fetch at once in single connection-synchronized operation.
    DBLookupTable
    Database table/SQLquery based lookup table which gets data by performing SQL query.
    RangeLookupTable
    Range lookup table contains records, which defines intervals, eg: Lookup table defined as follows:
    low_slow,0,10,0,50
    low_fast,0,10,50,100
    high_slow,10,20,0,50
    high_fast,10,20,50,100
    with startFields = {1,3} and endFields = {2,4} has 4 intervals with 2 searching parameters: first from interval 0-20, and second from interval 0-100.
    SimpleLookupTable
    Simple lookup table which reads data from flat file and creates Map structure.
